FlickMover
public static interface FlickMover.FlickListener

The listener interface for receiving flick events. The class that is interested in processing a flick event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addFlickListener method. When the flick event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.

See Also:
FlickEvent
